{"tid":55914,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得自己唔值得同好男仔一齊","createTime":"2016-12-26T18:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T07:19:38.000Z","uid":61147,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70998279f911ad1eeeef44c93cf535b034b6875d","tid":55914,"uid":61147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:28:02.000Z","msg":"話說琴日同我暗戀左一排嘅男仔whatsapp,到依家佢都再冇覆過我...<br />\n<br />\n我: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我:2016完之前可以問我幾個問題,我一定會講真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢:三圍係幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我:唔好玩啦認真啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢:你同你ex做過啲咩特別事?<br />\n我:咪又係嗰啲,行街睇戲食飯囉<br />\n佢:我係問有冇試過做啲咩曳野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我:你真係想知?<br />\n佢:你介意嘅話可以唔講...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我:um..講得嘅,我試過用手同用口幫佢<br />\n佢:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我:咁佢想同我做,我唔肯,佢話辛苦好難忍我先幫佢咋<br />\n佢:咁其實大學生有試過又唔係好出奇嘅...<br />\n佢:我瞓先啦,下次再傾<br />\n<br />\n其實佢係咪對我有feel先會介意我同第個男仔嘅事...<br />\n如果唔係佢點解會即刻話去瞓..定我諗多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同佢出過幾次街同埋去過佢hall過夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實慢慢諗下,佢嘅反應都好正常..如果佢真係對我有feel但佢知道左我試過幫男仔打飛機同含,佢反感都好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得自己好污蔑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人生可唔可以重頭黎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得我連普通男仔都襯唔上...仲要佢係一個好charm嘅男仔...<br />\n<br />\n利申:飛機 樣衰 唔收兵 <br />\n<br />\n識我嘅應該知 勿相認"},{"pid":"bfcd34989c221579324cc6bfdbc9202c707f5017","tid":55914,"uid":62754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38fa8d67e1308359a3e46621dbd2728e288dd5c2","tid":55914,"uid":727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:31:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ba1967f4d3053a6d5856f5318ff1e54d0e0d7c","tid":55914,"uid":61147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以回應下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21b793efad096d78ca5541ea34e629c6c45862a","tid":55914,"uid":61147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:32:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留低粒膠又唔講野係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c322f03946898fa8017a097fb3207cc0477a36","tid":55914,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:33:17.000Z","msg":"下次見到佢即刻幫佢含咪得"},{"pid":"b3b0e03bd590ab3afbef12fa1f58ffe4a660b0a3","tid":55914,"uid":59541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/iteqlnkb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fi