wn.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同佢出過幾次街同埋去過佢hall過夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實慢慢諗下,佢嘅反應都好正常..如果佢真係對我有feel但佢知道左我試過幫男仔打飛機同含,佢反感都好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得自己好污蔑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人生可唔可以重頭黎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得我連普通男仔都襯唔上...仲要佢係一個好charm嘅男仔...<br />\n<br />\n利申:飛機 樣衰 唔收兵 <br />\n<br />\n識我嘅應該知 勿相認</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試過相同情況 我本身追緊 一聽到話試過含撚我即刻收隊唔追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實我就唔介意女仔同人扑野 但唔該唔好講到好正常而且自己都唔care咁 男仔好反感 你自己都唔愛惜自己 有咩可能要求人地愛你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9afb19133dbeeaec789eb21ccf67ad354e39784","tid":55914,"uid":69215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:07:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我</span>:2016完之前可以問我幾個問題,我一定會講真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢</span>:三圍係幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我</span>:唔好玩啦認真啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢</span>:你同你ex做過啲咩特別事?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我</span>:咪又係嗰啲,行街睇戲食飯囉<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢</span>:我係問有冇試過做啲咩曳野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我</span>:你真係想知?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">